    Author:
    Mike Durbin This class is ignored until non-'readonly' federations are supported. At that time, include the following in the repository.json and remove the 'ignore' annotation. "federated-directory" : { "classname" : "org.fcrepo.connector.file.FedoraFileSystemConnector", "directoryPath" : "${fcrepo.test.dir1:must-be-provided}", "projections" : [ "default:/federated => /" ], "contentBasedSha1" : "false", "readonly" : false, "extraPropertiesStorage" : "json" },
